translate french izzy16_2245c52c:

    # moose "It looks fun to me. You ever play Trouble? Man, I fucking love Trouble."
    moose "Moi, ça a l’air marrant. T’as déjà joué à Trouble ? Mec, j’adore Trouble."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy16.rpy:105
